FORM CORR_MAINT_ZV_ZFITR004 USING VALUE(CM_ACTION) RC.
  DATA: RETCODE LIKE SY-SUBRC, COUNT TYPE I, TRSP_KEYLEN TYPE SYFLENG.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <TAB_KEY_X> TYPE X.
  CLEAR RC.
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-BUKRS TO
ZFITR004-BUKRS .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-FECHA_REM TO
ZFITR004-FECHA_REM .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-SECUENCIA TO
ZFITR004-SECUENCIA .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-BELNR TO
ZFITR004-BELNR .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-GJAHR TO
ZFITR004-GJAHR .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-XBLNR TO
ZFITR004-XBLNR .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-LIFNR TO
ZFITR004-LIFNR .
MOVE ZV_ZFITR004-MANDT TO
ZFITR004-MANDT .
  CORR_KEYTAB             =  E071K.
  CORR_KEYTAB-OBJNAME     = 'ZFITR004'.
  IF NOT <vim_corr_keyx> IS ASSIGNED.
    ASSIGN CORR_KEYTAB-TABKEY TO <vim_corr_keyx> CASTING.
  ENDIF.
  ASSIGN ZFITR004 TO <TAB_KEY_X> CASTING.
  PERFORM VIM_GET_TRSPKEYLEN
    USING 'ZFITR004'
    CHANGING TRSP_KEYLEN.
  <VIM_CORR_KEYX>(TRSP_KEYLEN) = <TAB_KEY_X>(TRSP_KEYLEN).
  PERFORM UPDATE_CORR_KEYTAB USING CM_ACTION RETCODE.
  ADD: RETCODE TO RC, 1 TO COUNT.
  IF RC LT COUNT AND CM_ACTION NE PRUEFEN.
    CLEAR RC.
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.
